---
---
<section id="community" class="section community-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="community-grid">
      <div class="community-intro">
        <span class="badge badge-maroon">Get Involved</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">An active lab for student creators</h2>
        <p class="community-desc">
          uplb.tools serves as a collaborative sandbox. We welcome all UPLB students interested in design, engineering, or documentation.
        </p>
        
        <div class="roles-list">
          <div class="role-item">
            <div class="role-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"></polyline>
                <polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="role-text">
              <h4>Software Engineering</h4>
              <p>Contribute to codebases built with Astro, React, and Vite. Learn clean repository architecture, Git flows, and review cycles.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="role-item">
            <div class="role-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="21"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="role-text">
              <h4>UI / UX Design</h4>
              <p>Wireframe layouts, model workflows, and construct design tokens. Make tools responsive, accessible, and clean.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="role-item">
            <div class="role-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path>
                <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
                <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line>
                <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="role-text">
              <h4>Documentation & Copy</h4>
              <p>Write setup guidelines, draft release logs, compile instructions, and explain how to install our browser extensions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="community-links">
        <!-- GitHub Link Card -->
        <div class="card link-card github-card">
          <div class="link-card-header">
            <h3>GitHub Organization</h3>
            <span class="status status-active">Active Repositories</span>
          </div>
          <p>Request an invitation to the organization, browse open issues, or review our pull requests.</p>
          <a href="https://github.com/uplbtools" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">
            <span>Explore on GitHub</span>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Discord Link Card -->
        <div class="card link-card">
          <div class="link-card-header">
            <h3>Discord Server</h3>
            <span class="status status-tba">TBA</span>
          </div>
          <p>Join chats to brainstorm ideas, ask technical questions, and coordinate code modifications.</p>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" disabled>
            <span>TBA</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Messenger Link Card -->
        <div class="card link-card">
          <div class="link-card-header">
            <h3>Messenger Chat</h3>
            <span class="status status-tba">TBA</span>
          </div>
          <p>Informal coordinator chat for UPLB organization members to host quick standups.</p>
          <button class="btn btn-secondary" disabled>
            <span>TBA</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .community-section {
    background-color: #090b11;
  }
  
  .community-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .community-desc {
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-body);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .roles-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }
  
  .role-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  
  .role-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background-color: #171923;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--text-title);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .role-text h4 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .role-text p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }
  
  .community-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .link-card {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
  }
  
  .link-card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .link-card-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .status {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  
  .status-active {
    color: var(--brand-green-light);
  }
  
  .status-tba {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .link-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-body);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .link-card .btn {
    width: 100%;
  }
  
  .github-card {
    border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
  }
  
  .github-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--brand-maroon-light);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .community-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
